title: DisplayFusion Pro 8.1.2 + Portable + Keygen - Crackingpatching
description:
Description: 
DisplayFusion 8.1.2 Final + Portable 9.0 Beta 4 An excellent program for managing your desktop wallpaper. Able to search and install new wallpapers, plus you can set the interval through which they will be automatically changed, you can download DisplayFusion below. 
It should be noted that users with a multi-monitor system will be able to install separately on each monitor the wallpaper they want, it can be called one of the main features of this product, because as far as you should know, such a trick can not be done by standard Windows tools. 
DisplayFusion has an extended multi-monitor taskbar support, you can put different wallpapers on each monitor, you can select a folder and pictures from there randomly will be installed on the desktop, you can also transfer the active window using the keyboard to another monitor, there is support for searching and downloading wallpaper with the service Flickr and Vladstudio. 

Developer: Binary Fortress Software 
License: ShareWare 
Language: Multi + Russian 
Size: 55 + 20 MB 
OS: Windows
